---
import { Image } from "astro:assets";
import logoGDGCbba from "../assets/images/logoGDGCbba.png";
---

<article>
  <section
    class="banner flex aspect-[1408/874] w-full flex-col items-center justify-center gap-10 bg-cover bg-center bg-no-repeat md:m-0 md:bg-cover md:p-0"
  >
    <Image
      class="-mt-5 w-[220px] md:mt-0 md:w-[500px]"
      src={logoGDGCbba}
      alt="logo GDG"
    />

    <p
      class="hidden max-w-xl px-1 text-center text-2xl font-normal not-italic md:block"
    >
      Somos un grupo centrado en compartir conocimiento sobre las tecnolog√≠as de


      <a class="" href="https://gdg.community.dev/gdg-cochabamba/">Google</a>.
    </p>
  </section>
</article>

<style>
  .banner {
    background-image: url("../assets/images/fondoHero.png");
    background-size: cover;
    /* aspect-ratio: 1408/874; */
    aspect-ratio: 16/9;
  }

  p {
    color: var(--neutral-grey, var(--neutral-grey-light, #5f6368));
    font-family:
      Google Sans,
      sans-serif;
  }

  a {
    color: #4285f4;
  }
</style>
